text: Cuauthémoc Muñoz (born 18 May 1961) is a Mexican former cyclist. He competed in the team time trial event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Mexico Category:Cyclists at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
